1
00:02:43,496 --> 00:02:45,915
嘿,西奥。这里太黑了。
Hey, Theo. It's so dark in here.

2
00:02:48,918 --> 00:02:51,338
-你在施魔法吗?——没有。
- You doin' some magic? - No.

3
00:02:51,421 --> 00:02:53,673
是啊，我有一段时间没看过你表演魔术了。
Yeah, I haven't seen you do any tricks in a while.

4
00:02:54,299 --> 00:02:56,926
好吧，我想我会忘记寄给你的邮件。
Well, guess I'll forget about what came in the mail for you.

5
00:02:57,010 --> 00:02:58,595
我的邮件里有什么?
What came in the mail for me?

6
00:02:58,678 --> 00:03:02,390
你被邀请来参加这个地方…魔法学院。
You've been invited to attend this place... The Institute of Magic.

7
00:03:02,849 --> 00:03:05,894
它在山上。这是一个为期五周的强化学习。
It's up in the mountains. It's a five-week intensive study where...

8
00:03:05,977 --> 00:03:08,355
我知道魔法学院是什么了。
I know what the Institute of Magic is.

9
00:03:08,438 --> 00:03:10,857
爸爸和我经常谈论这件事。
Dad and I used to talk about it all the time.

10
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:23,870
你内心有个声音，这个声音在说，
There's a voice inside of you, and it's the voice that says,

11
00:03:23,953 --> 00:03:26,790
“我想成为一个魔术师。”
"I want to be a magician."

12
00:03:27,374 --> 00:03:28,375
你好,西奥。
Hello, Theo.

13
00:03:28,458 --> 00:03:29,876
他怎么知道我的名字的?
How did he know my name?

14
00:03:29,959 --> 00:03:33,004
我怎么知道你的名字?你的申请表上有。
How did I know your name? It was on your application.

15
00:03:33,088 --> 00:03:38,510
西奥，我是国家宝藏罗伊·普雷斯顿，我也听到了声音。
Theo, I'm national treasure Roy Preston, and I hear voices too.

16
00:03:38,593 --> 00:03:42,722
三年前，我成立了魔法学院，
Shribbity-three-ish years ago, I founded the Institute of Magic,

17
00:03:42,806 --> 00:03:45,642
为有前途的年轻魔术师而设的音乐学院。
a conservatory for promising young magicians.

18
00:03:45,725 --> 00:03:50,313
在这里，世界著名的魔术师将教你七种魔术。
Here, world-famous magicians will teach you the seven types of magic.

19
00:03:50,730 --> 00:03:51,940
花招。
Sleight of hand.

20
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,361
预测。
Prediction.

21
00:04:00,031 --> 00:04:01,032
恢复。
Restoration.

22
00:04:01,116 --> 00:04:04,994
消失……和外表。
Vanish... and appearance.

23
00:04:05,078 --> 00:04:07,497
固体……通过固体。
Solid... through solid.

24
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:10,709
逃跑。
Escape.

25
00:04:12,252 --> 00:04:13,545
悬浮。
Levitation.

26
00:04:13,628 --> 00:04:15,588
然后你就可以表演了
And you will get to perform

27
00:04:15,672 --> 00:04:19,259
在世界著名的罗伊·普雷斯顿纪念剧院。
in the world-famous Roy Preston Prememorial Theater.

28
00:04:19,342 --> 00:04:23,221
你会和其他年轻的魔术师建立持久的关系。
And you'll build lasting relationships with other young magicians.

29
00:04:23,304 --> 00:04:27,267
即使是那些奇怪的。因为在这里，我们都是怪胎。
Even the weird ones. Because here, we're all the weird ones.

30
00:04:29,102 --> 00:04:31,521
哇。很酷的鸟,兰德尔。
Wow. Cool bird, Randall.

31
00:04:31,604 --> 00:04:34,858
但不要相信我的话。今年夏天你自己来看看吧。
But don't take my word for it. Come see for yourself this summer.

32
00:04:39,487 --> 00:04:41,364
魔法营听起来很酷吧?
Magic camp sounds pretty cool?

33
00:04:41,448 --> 00:04:44,492
这不是“魔法营”。是魔法学院。
It's not "magic camp." It's the Institute of Magic.

34
00:04:44,576 --> 00:04:46,286
这完全是著名的。
It's totally famous.

35
00:04:46,369 --> 00:04:48,621
但我不知道。
But I don't know.

36
00:04:50,206 --> 00:04:51,875
今年夏天我应该呆在家里。
I should stay home this summer.

37
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:57,297
你需要我来修剪草坪和招待卡梅隆
You need me to mow the lawn and to entertain Cameron.

38
00:04:57,380 --> 00:05:00,008
我很好。而且你也没那么有趣。
I'm fine. And you're not that entertaining.

39
00:05:01,051 --> 00:05:05,388
我想你可能对这个感兴趣，但如果你不感兴趣，也没关系。
I thought you might be interested in this, but if you're not, that's okay.

40
00:05:06,181 --> 00:05:07,599
等待。
Wait.

41
00:05:08,975 --> 00:05:11,144
爸爸总是说他想让我去那里。
Dad always said he wanted me to go there.

42
00:05:11,853 --> 00:05:15,732
他以前一定申请过我……你知道的。
He must have applied for me before... you know.

43
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:20,612
如果爸爸肯花时间帮我申请，我也许应该……
If Dad took the time to apply for me, I should probably...

44
00:05:20,695 --> 00:05:23,114
你可以花整个夏天修剪草坪，
You could spend the summer mowing the lawn,

45
00:05:23,907 --> 00:05:27,327
或者你可以和世界上最伟大的魔术师一起学习魔术。
or you can study magic with the world's greatest magicians.

46
00:05:33,958 --> 00:05:36,378
-你有票吗?——亲爱的。
- Do you have the tickets? - Honey.

47
00:05:36,461 --> 00:05:38,713
-不，我没有票。-你拿到票了!
- No, I don't have the tickets. - You have the tickets!

48
00:05:40,382 --> 00:05:43,885
“这一代最伟大的魔术师。”是的,对的。
"This generation's greatest magician." Yeah, right.

49
00:05:43,968 --> 00:05:45,929
我们在里约热内卢电视台看到Penn和Teller。
We're seeing Penn and Teller at the Rio.

50
00:05:46,012 --> 00:05:47,097
太好了。
Great.

51
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:51,393
-昨晚我们看到了克里斯·达伍德。——头脑吹。
- Last night we saw Kris Darkwood. - Minds blown.

52
00:05:51,476 --> 00:05:54,521
然后黑木让凯撒的大卫雕像完全消失了。
And then Darkwood made the David statue at Caesars totally disappear.

53
00:05:54,604 --> 00:05:55,980
我的头还在爆炸。
My head is still exploding.

54
00:05:56,690 --> 00:06:01,027
克里斯汀娜·达伍德在维加斯有最令人兴奋的表演。
Kristina Darkwood has the most mind-blowing show in Vegas.

55
00:06:01,111 --> 00:06:03,822
这不是令人兴奋的。你的头不会爆炸，我保证。
It's not mind-blowing. Your head will not explode, I promise you.

56
00:06:07,617 --> 00:06:10,745
天啊。这里面有什么?
Geez. What do you got in this thing?

57
00:06:11,413 --> 00:06:12,872
汤!
Soup!

58
00:06:12,956 --> 00:06:16,960
我很抱歉。我发誓我有一张20美元的钞票。
I'm so sorry. I swear I had a 20-dollar bill in here.

59
00:06:17,919 --> 00:06:22,382
它去了哪里?也许在这里。我去找找看。
Where did it go? Maybe it's in here. I'll look for it.

60
00:06:22,465 --> 00:06:25,010
我的。不，不在这里。
My. No, it's not here.

61
00:06:25,093 --> 00:06:27,721
在这儿。
Here it is.

62
00:06:27,804 --> 00:06:30,807
——找到它。!谢天谢地。
- Found it. ! Thank heavens.

63
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:34,269
我可以要回12美元吗?
Can I have $12 back?

64
00:06:39,357 --> 00:06:41,276
上次我试着做个好人。
Last time I try to be a nice guy.

65
00:06:41,359 --> 00:06:43,319
“好”可能有点言过其实了。
"Nice" may be an overstatement.

66
00:06:44,904 --> 00:06:48,199
罗伊。嘿。你在这里做什么?
Roy. Hey. What are you doing here?

67
00:06:48,908 --> 00:06:49,909
拉斯维加斯,宝贝。
Vegas, baby.

68
00:06:50,410 --> 00:06:53,872
另外，你能送我到希望街123号吗?
Also, can you take me to 123 Hope Street, please?

69
00:06:56,875 --> 00:06:58,084
安迪，生意怎么样?
So, Andy, how's business?

70
00:06:58,168 --> 00:07:00,337
生活的梦想。
Living the dream.

71
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:03,631
我刚学会了一个叫做“Uber把我的工资减半”的新把戏。
I just learned this awesome new trick called "Uber cuts my paychecks in half."

72
00:07:04,799 --> 00:07:09,095
嗯，你很幸运，因为今年夏天我有一个顾问空缺。
Well, you are in luck because I have a counselor opening this summer.

73
00:07:09,179 --> 00:07:12,265
大卫·布莱恩退出了，你是我想到的第一个名字。
David Blaine dropped out, and you were the first name I thought of.

74
00:07:12,349 --> 00:07:13,350
——真的吗?-是的。
- Really? - Yeah.

75
00:07:13,433 --> 00:07:16,353
大卫·布莱恩退出了，我是名单上的第二个名字。
David Blaine drops out, and I'm the second name on the list.

76
00:07:16,436 --> 00:07:18,646
我从没说过你是名单上的第二名。
I never said you were the second name on the list.

77
00:07:18,730 --> 00:07:20,857
我说你是我想到的第一个人。
I said you were the first person I thought of.

78
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:22,525
你是…
You were...

79
00:07:22,609 --> 00:07:24,694
你在名单上排名很靠后。
You were pretty far down there on the list.

80
00:07:24,778 --> 00:07:28,365
我很欣赏你的直率诚实，但我不再施魔法了。
Well, I appreciate your blunt honesty, but I don't do magic anymore.

81
00:07:28,448 --> 00:07:30,784
我已经很长时间没有了。用黑木制作自…
I haven't for a long time. Ever since Darkwood...

82
00:07:30,867 --> 00:07:34,496
是的。我很抱歉，我不怪你。
Yes. I'm so sorry and I-I don't blame you.

83
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:36,664
——真的吗?——没有。
- Really? - No.

84
00:07:36,748 --> 00:07:39,876
你不能全心全意地爱上魔术
You cannot love magic with your whole heart

85
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:41,961
直到你的心再次完整。
until your heart is whole again.

86
00:07:42,045 --> 00:07:45,924
这就是……与魔法有关的陈词滥调听起来很深奥
And there it is... the magic-related clichés which sound profound

87
00:07:46,007 --> 00:07:47,425
但实际上毫无意义。
but are actually meaningless.

88
00:07:47,509 --> 00:07:50,512
你知道，我会想念那些，但我还是不会回来。
You know, I'm gonna miss those, but I'm still not coming back.

89
00:07:51,971 --> 00:07:54,224
Kris将在今年夏天回归。
Kris is coming back this summer.

90
00:07:54,849 --> 00:07:56,768
用黑木制作- - - - - - ?-克里斯·达伍德，是的。
- Darkwood? - Kris Darkwood, yeah.

91
00:07:57,435 --> 00:08:00,730
所以她会有她自己的小屋我也会有我自己的小屋?
So she would have her own cabin and I would have my own cabin?

92
00:08:00,814 --> 00:08:04,776
你们两个都将与年轻的魔术师紧密合作。
Both of you will be working very closely with the, young magicians.

93
00:08:04,859 --> 00:08:08,822
那大礼帽呢?你现在还这么做，对吧?这是一间小屋对一间小屋，胜者全得?
And the Top Hat? You still do that, right? It's cabin versus cabin, winner takes all?

94
00:08:08,905 --> 00:08:11,866
是的，我的意思是，你知道高帽比赛是怎么运作的。
Yes, I mean, you know how the Top Hat competition works.

95
00:08:15,453 --> 00:08:19,833
哦，Weiners的世界。好了。希望您预订了房间。
Ooh, World Of Weiners. Nice. Hope you got a reservation.

96
00:08:21,001 --> 00:08:23,128
不管怎样，想一想。
Anyway, think about it.

97
00:08:23,211 --> 00:08:25,922
因为我知道你还能让他们走…
Because I know you can still make 'em go...

98
00:08:30,635 --> 00:08:31,845
“哇。”
"Wow."

99
00:08:36,683 --> 00:08:38,643
那家伙很好。
That guy is good.

100
00:08:38,727 --> 00:08:40,729
忘记了我的电话。你能把我的电话递给我吗?
Forgot my phone. Can you hand me my phone?

101
00:08:40,812 --> 00:08:43,273
哦。那将是一个非常酷的退出。
Ooh. That would have been a really cool exit.

102
00:08:43,356 --> 00:08:47,485
你知道我买了多少热狗他们才会让我这么做吗?
You know how many hot dogs I had to buy so they would let me do that to the sign?

103
00:08:47,569 --> 00:08:51,990
一百年。我也不会骄傲地说我吃了14个。
A hundred. And I'm not proud to say I ate 14 of them.

104
00:09:00,832 --> 00:09:03,001
-给你。-玩得开心，保罗。
- Here it is. - Have fun, Paul.

105
00:09:05,545 --> 00:09:08,006
——获得乐趣。女孩,再见。再见!
- Have fun. - Bye-bye girls. Bye!

106
00:09:08,089 --> 00:09:09,090
再见!
Bye!

107
00:09:10,383 --> 00:09:12,719
这些都是世界闻名的魔术师吗?
These are all world-famous magicians?

108
00:09:13,887 --> 00:09:16,723
-他们看起来像一群ner…-要交新朋友。
- They look like a bunch of ner... - New friends to make.

109
00:09:16,806 --> 00:09:18,266
再告诉我一遍。
Tell me one more time.

110
00:09:18,350 --> 00:09:21,519
毒葛有三个杏仁状的小叶，颜色从浅绿色到红色，
Poison ivy has three almond-shaped leaflets, light green to red in color,

111
00:09:21,603 --> 00:09:23,104
常在水源附近发现。
often found near a water source.

112
00:09:23,188 --> 00:09:26,316
经常，但不总是，内森。来吧，把你的脑袋放进去!
Often but not always, Nathan. Come on, get your head in the game!

113
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:29,110
妈妈，爸爸，我有我的肾上腺素注射器，我的费内根
Mother, Father, I've got my EpiPen, my Phenergan,

114
00:09:29,194 --> 00:09:31,780
我的手镯上用十种语言写着"花生过敏"
my bracelet that says "peanut allergy" in ten languages.

115
00:09:31,863 --> 00:09:34,699
还有我的尿滤器以防我被困在什么地方
Plus I have my uropathy filter in case I get stranded somewhere

116
00:09:34,783 --> 00:09:36,493
还得喝自己的尿
and have to drink my own pee.

117
00:09:36,576 --> 00:09:37,952
我们已经尽力了。
We've done all we can.

118
00:09:38,036 --> 00:09:40,455
记住，不要害怕任何事情。
Remember, don't be afraid of anything.

119
00:09:40,538 --> 00:09:42,874
凡事都要害怕。
Be afraid of everything.

120
00:09:44,042 --> 00:09:47,128
兔子在哪里?第一次拥抱是什么时候?
Where are the bunnies? And what time is the first cuddle?

121
00:09:48,171 --> 00:09:50,173
我也喜欢兔子。
I love bunnies too.

122
00:09:50,256 --> 00:09:51,466
他们是美味的。
They're delicious.

123
00:09:53,009 --> 00:09:55,261
来吧,儿子。
Come on, son.

124
00:09:57,222 --> 00:09:59,808
爸爸，我真的必须戴这个领结吗?
Dad, do I really have to wear this bow tie?

125
00:09:59,891 --> 00:10:02,018
就像脖子上挂着"踢我"的牌子。
It's like wearing a "kick me" sign on my neck.

126
00:10:02,102 --> 00:10:05,271
没有领结，你只是另一个魔术师。
Without that bow tie, you are just another magician.

127
00:10:05,355 --> 00:10:09,484
但你是科尔内留斯·凯斯勒的儿子…神奇的皇室。
But you're Kornelius Kessler's son... Magic royalty.

128
00:10:09,567 --> 00:10:11,695
记住，只有金魔杖才有用。
Now remember, nothing but the Golden Wand will do.

129
00:10:12,612 --> 00:10:14,372
如果你需要我，我会在密苏里州的布兰森。
If you need me, I'll be in Branson, Missouri.

130
00:10:15,156 --> 00:10:18,243
你父亲让我告诉你要好好玩。
Your father instructed me to tell you to have a good time.

131
00:10:18,326 --> 00:10:19,994
他还要求我把这个给你。
He also asked that I give you this.

132
00:10:22,247 --> 00:10:24,290
你妈妈让我给你这个。
And your mother asked that I give you this.

133
00:10:24,874 --> 00:10:25,875
一,二。
One, two.

134
00:10:27,085 --> 00:10:28,795
詹妮尔，和往常一样，我必须请求你
And, Janelle, as always, I must request,

135
00:10:28,878 --> 00:10:31,023
既然是我来找你，
since I would be the one who would have to come find you,

136
00:10:31,047 --> 00:10:34,300
请不要像在其他营地那样逃跑。
please don't run away like you have at so many other camps.

137
00:10:34,384 --> 00:10:36,011
也许你可以试着参与进来。
Maybe you could even try to participate.

138
00:10:36,553 --> 00:10:38,096
我不作任何承诺，汉密尔顿。
I make no promises, Hamilton.

139
00:10:38,930 --> 00:10:41,266
也许我们可以试着让这种态度消失。
Maybe we can try and make that attitude disappear.

140
00:10:47,355 --> 00:10:50,817
宝贝，安迪·达克曼回来了!
Andy Duckerman is back, baby!

141
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:59,051
-嘿，你去哪?我就在这里。——用黑木制作它!
- Hey, where you going? I'm right here. - It's Darkwood!

142
00:10:59,075 --> 00:11:01,619
这就跟你问声好！你好吗?嗨。谢谢你！
Hi! How are you? Hi. Thank you.

143
00:11:01,703 --> 00:11:05,206
嗨。嗨。你们喜欢魔术吗?
Hi. Hi. Do you guys like magic?

144
00:11:05,290 --> 00:11:06,833
是啊!
Yeah!

145
00:11:20,472 --> 00:11:21,848
我还得签到。
I still have to sign in.

146
00:11:21,931 --> 00:11:25,602
我不知道我是否属于这里。我只是在房间里玩牌。
I don't know if I belong here. I just play with cards in my room.

147
00:11:25,685 --> 00:11:27,937
我知道你很害怕
I know you're scared,

148
00:11:28,021 --> 00:11:29,898
但要记住你最初来这里的原因。
but remember why you came in the first place.

149
00:11:31,608 --> 00:11:33,651
亲爱的，我也想他。
Honey, I miss him too.

150
00:11:34,527 --> 00:11:36,321
但让我问你一件事。
But let me ask you one thing.

151
00:11:37,405 --> 00:11:39,032
你喜欢魔术吗?
Do you love magic?

152
00:11:43,161 --> 00:11:45,372
我们能不能趁我还没被人逮到之前离开这里?
Can we get outta here before I get any geek on me?

153
00:11:46,373 --> 00:11:47,874
别担心你的房间。
Don't worry about your room.

154
00:11:47,957 --> 00:11:50,293
我不会同时有超过十个朋友在那里。
I'll never have more than ten friends in there at one time.

155
00:11:50,377 --> 00:11:52,879
传说许多年前，
Legend holds that many years ago,

