00:29:28,643 --> 00:29:32,355
现在，你明白了，这是一个为想学魔术的孩子们准备的训练营，
Now, you understand that this is a camp for children who wanna learn magic,

474
00:29:32,439 --> 00:29:33,648
而你是来教他们的。
and you're here to teach them.

475
00:29:33,732 --> 00:29:35,692
普雷斯顿，这些孩子，他们没救了。
Preston, these kids, they're hopeless.

476
00:29:35,775 --> 00:29:37,736
内森被海绵球噎住了。
Nathan choked on a sponge ball.

477
00:29:37,819 --> 00:29:41,197
露丝连一只兔子都不敢碰。她喜欢兔子。
Ruth can't even touch a bunny. And she loves bunnies.

478
00:29:41,281 --> 00:29:43,366
他们甚至连最基本的纸牌把戏都玩不出来。
They can't even pull off the most basic card trick.

479
00:29:43,450 --> 00:29:46,286
但是你看，一个你不相信的把戏是把戏，
But you see, a trick that you don't believe is a trick,

480
00:29:46,369 --> 00:29:47,579
这是最好的技巧。
that's the best trick of all.

481
00:29:47,662 --> 00:29:49,222
这就是你要给我的建议?
That's the advice you're gonna give me?

482
00:29:49,247 --> 00:29:51,082
只是一些普通的魔法谚语
Just more generic magical proverbs

483
00:29:51,166 --> 00:29:54,294
这听起来很有意义，但完全是无稽之谈?
that sound meaningful but are total nonsense?

484
00:29:54,377 --> 00:29:57,672
安迪，只有这样才能创造更多的魔法
Andy, the only way to create more magic in the world

485
00:29:57,756 --> 00:30:00,091
不是通过创造更多的魔法。
is not by creating more magic.

486
00:30:00,175 --> 00:30:02,594
——是的。就像这样。-安迪，让我说完
- Yep. Just like that. - Andy, let me finish.

487
00:30:02,677 --> 00:30:03,845
-不，我受够了。——这是…
- No, I'm done. - It's...

488
00:30:03,928 --> 00:30:07,474
对不起，普雷斯顿，我受够了。我离开这里。好吧?
I'm sorry, Preston, but I'm done. I'm outta here. Okay?

489
00:30:10,435 --> 00:30:11,436
愚蠢的。
Stupid.

490
00:30:12,395 --> 00:30:14,314
我做得很好。
I was doing perfectly fine.

491
00:30:14,689 --> 00:30:19,069
嗯,不是很好。我在做好事。good-ish。排序的。
Well, not great. I was doing good. Was doing good-ish. Sort of.

492
00:30:33,500 --> 00:30:35,126
我可能错了，
I could be mistaken,

493
00:30:35,919 --> 00:30:40,340
但我记得我看到过一个12岁的孩子用一只手完美地跳法罗牌。
but I think I saw a 12-year-old execute a perfect faro shuffle with one hand.

494
00:30:40,423 --> 00:30:41,591
我只是在鬼混。
I was just fooling around.

495
00:30:41,675 --> 00:30:45,804
法罗洗牌是单手最难的纸牌技巧之一，
A faro shuffle is one of the single most difficult card skills with two hands,

496
00:30:45,887 --> 00:30:47,972
我想你们只是用了一个。
and you just did it with one, I think.

497
00:30:48,431 --> 00:30:50,517
-再来一次。-我不想。
- Do it again. - I don't want to.

498
00:30:50,600 --> 00:30:53,311
——为什么不呢?你做到了。-我害怕。
- Why not? You just did it. - I get scared.

499
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:58,358
-怕什么?-我不知道。人们看着我。
- Scared of what? - I don't know. People looking at me.

500
00:30:59,401 --> 00:31:01,820
无论如何,很愚蠢。只是…
Anyway, it's stupid. Just...

501
00:31:01,903 --> 00:31:03,613
你知道那是什么吗?
You know what that is?

502
00:31:03,697 --> 00:31:05,323
这就是怯场。
That is stage fright.

503
00:31:05,657 --> 00:31:08,785
进入你的脑海。对于一个魔术师来说，这是一个怪异的地方。
Gets in your head. And that is a freaky place for a magician to be.

504
00:31:09,244 --> 00:31:12,747
-你以前也这样吗?——没有。别荒谬。
- It's happened to you before? - No. Don't be ridiculous.

505
00:31:12,831 --> 00:31:15,250
虽然，我是一个受欢迎的专业人士。
Although, I am an acclaimed professional.

506
00:31:15,333 --> 00:31:19,796
而你，在另一方面，是一个可以做完美的法罗洗牌的业余选手。
You, on the other hand, are a rank amateur who can somehow do a perfect faro shuffle.

507
00:31:19,879 --> 00:31:21,464
让我看看。
So let me see it.

508
00:31:22,298 --> 00:31:24,443
-就像我说的…-假装我不在这里。别看我。
- Like I said... - Pretend I'm not here. Don't look at me.

509
00:31:24,467 --> 00:31:26,761
保持洗牌。保持牌的移动。好吧?
Keep shuffling. Keep the cards moving. Okay?

510
00:31:27,929 --> 00:31:29,681
你从哪里来?
So where you from?

511
00:31:30,765 --> 00:31:32,517
兰开斯特,加州。
Lancaster, California.

512
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:33,810
这听起来……
That sounds...

513
00:31:34,978 --> 00:31:37,564
实际上，这听起来很无聊。我不会骗你的。
That sounds boring, actually. I'm not gonna lie to you.

514
00:31:37,647 --> 00:31:39,983
没关系。可能有点无聊。
It's okay. Maybe a little boring.

515
00:31:40,775 --> 00:31:43,903
我们住在爱德华兹空军基地附近。很多军人家庭。
We live near Edwards Air Force Base. Lot of military families.

516
00:31:44,320 --> 00:31:45,905
你爸爸在服役吗?
Is your dad in the service?

517
00:31:45,989 --> 00:31:47,365
他是。
He was.

518
00:31:48,074 --> 00:31:50,952
这些是他的卡片。
Um, these were his cards.

519
00:31:52,454 --> 00:31:55,957
嘿!你有兄弟姐妹吗?
Hey! Do you have any brothers or sisters?

520
00:31:56,332 --> 00:31:59,669
我有个小弟弟叫卡梅隆。他是最坏的打算。
I have a little brother named Cameron. He's the worst.

521
00:31:59,753 --> 00:32:02,130
——超级烦人吗?——是的,完全。
- Super annoying? - Yeah, totally.

522
00:32:02,547 --> 00:32:05,842
老兄,你很棒。让我看看你的套路。
Dude, you're great. Show me your routine.

523
00:32:06,593 --> 00:32:09,387
好吧。拿张卡就行了。
Okay. Um, just take a card.

524
00:32:10,055 --> 00:32:12,724
好吧。
All right.

525
00:32:12,807 --> 00:32:14,309
现在帮我把它放在最上面。
Now put it on top for me.

526
00:32:15,143 --> 00:32:16,144
好吧。
Okay.

527
00:32:17,020 --> 00:32:18,021
,嗯…
And, um...

528
00:32:21,941 --> 00:32:23,943
嘿,放松。
Hey, relax.

529
00:32:24,027 --> 00:32:26,112
只有你和我。
It's just you and me.

530
00:32:26,196 --> 00:32:27,822
好吧,再试一次。
Okay, try again.

531
00:32:30,617 --> 00:32:31,951
放松。
Relax.

532
00:32:32,452 --> 00:32:34,162
只有你和我。
It's just you and me.

533
00:32:39,417 --> 00:32:41,920
好，方块3。
Okay, three of diamonds.

534
00:32:43,004 --> 00:32:45,799
“凯?把它放进去。
'Kay? Just gonna put that in there.

535
00:32:45,882 --> 00:32:48,426
-现在你能帮我把它塞进去吗?——确定。
- Now can you just tuck it in for me? - Sure.

536
00:32:51,888 --> 00:32:53,056
这是你的卡吗?
Is this your card?

537
00:32:53,139 --> 00:32:55,934
我的上帝,西奥!
My God, Theo!

538
00:32:56,017 --> 00:32:57,644
你是惊人的。
You are amazing.

539
00:32:58,269 --> 00:33:00,021
不，我只是知道一些技巧。
Nah, I just know some tricks.

540
00:33:00,105 --> 00:33:02,065
不，你是个魔术师。
No, you are a magician.

541
00:33:02,899 --> 00:33:05,402
——谢谢。-我能搞定的。
- Thanks. - I can work with this.

542
00:33:05,485 --> 00:33:07,529
可惜你的同屋都没用。
Too bad your bunkmates are so useless.

543
00:33:07,612 --> 00:33:11,991
内森是个数字天才，而贾德知道很多…
Nathan is a genius with numbers, and Judd knows a lot about...

544
00:33:12,075 --> 00:33:15,203
我们现在得去你的铺位好好谈谈。我们走吧。来吧。
We need to have a little talk with your bunk right now. Let's go. Come on.

545
00:33:15,620 --> 00:33:16,788
伙计们,嘿。
Guys, hey.

546
00:33:16,871 --> 00:33:20,166
如果我告诉你我们至少有机会了呢
What if I told you we have at least some semblance of a shot

547
00:33:20,250 --> 00:33:21,668
赢得高顶帽比赛?
to win the Top Hat competition?

548
00:33:21,751 --> 00:33:24,045
我得说我的血糖非常低。
I'd say my blood sugar is really low.

549
00:33:24,129 --> 00:33:28,091
不,我是认真的。西奥显然是个秘密红衣主教
No, I'm serious. Theo is apparently a secret Cardini,

550
00:33:28,174 --> 00:33:31,803
他告诉我，你们没有我想的那么烂。
and he tells me that you guys don't suck half as bad as I thought.

551
00:33:32,345 --> 00:33:35,598
我觉得很难相信，但别把他当成骗子。
Which I find hard to believe, but let's not make a liar out of him.

552
00:33:35,682 --> 00:33:38,518
你是在耍我们是在惩罚我们对魔法的精通吗?
Are you messing with us as a punishment for being awful at magic?

553
00:33:38,601 --> 00:33:41,771
我是认真的。作为三次金棒冠军和…
I'm serious. As a three-time Golden Wand winner and...

554
00:33:41,855 --> 00:33:44,065
等待。你赢得了金魔杖?
Wait. You won the Golden Wand?

555
00:33:44,149 --> 00:33:45,817
我们听到。现在我们可以吃饭了吗?
We've heard. Now can we eat?

556
00:33:45,900 --> 00:33:49,029
-马上。我解决你。-你能在我们吃饭的时候称呼我们吗?
- In a second. I'm addressing you. - Can you address us while we eat?

557
00:33:49,112 --> 00:33:52,991
不,不。这整个激动人心的演讲是我先想象出来的。
No, no. I had envisioned this whole rousing speech thing first.

558
00:33:53,074 --> 00:33:56,703
在你教我们之前，你不能做所有的振奋人心的演讲。
You don't get to do the whole rousing speech thing until you teach us stuff.

559
00:33:56,786 --> 00:33:58,705
好吧,公平点。但请听我说完。
Okay, fair point. But hear me out.

560
00:33:58,788 --> 00:34:01,875
如果我们能找到你不太臭的地方，
If we can find the areas where you don't totally stink,

561
00:34:01,958 --> 00:34:05,086
我可以把你们训练成像样的魔术师。
I can train you to be sort of decent magicians.

562
00:34:05,170 --> 00:34:09,841
有了西奥的技术，我们也许能打败黑木队。
And with Theo's skills, we might actually be able to beat Darkwood.

563
00:34:10,592 --> 00:34:13,720
我的意思是，赢得高顶帽比赛!
I mean, win the Top Hat competition!

564
00:34:13,803 --> 00:34:15,096
我是谁?
Who's with me?

565
00:34:15,180 --> 00:34:18,892
好了，这就是你们开始说“安迪!安迪!”
Okay, this is where you guys start going, "Andy! Andy!"

566
00:34:18,975 --> 00:34:20,518
如果我们说好，我们能吃吗?
If we say yes, can we eat?

567
00:34:21,895 --> 00:34:22,896
——是的!——好的。
- Yes! - Okay.

568
00:34:22,979 --> 00:34:26,608
——最后。-加油吧。我们有工作要做。
- Finally. - Let's fuel up. We got work to do.

569
00:34:26,691 --> 00:34:28,109
走向我。
Walk towards me.

570
00:34:28,777 --> 00:34:31,488
不要太僵硬，好吗?自然地行走。
Not so stiff, okay? Walk naturally.

571
00:34:31,571 --> 00:34:33,782
握住你的手，就好像你的手是空的。
Hold your hands as if they're actually empty.

572
00:34:35,992 --> 00:34:39,579
现在它们实际上是空的。来吧,伙计们。这是手掌101。
Now they are actually empty. Come on, guys. This is Palming 101.

573
00:34:40,747 --> 00:34:42,999
内森，别告诉我你对Tsum过敏。
Nathan, don't tell me you're allergic to Tsum Tsums.

574
00:34:43,083 --> 00:34:45,126
不。但我对灰尘过敏。
No. But I'm allergic to dirt.

575
00:34:45,210 --> 00:34:49,631
好了，伙计们，我们要让紧身衣更上一层楼。
Okay, guys, we are taking it to the next level with straitjackets.

576
00:34:49,714 --> 00:34:52,342
你知道，这真的很好。有点像拥抱。
You know, this is nice, actually. It's kind of like a hug.

577
00:34:52,884 --> 00:34:55,345
-是的，不是吗?-嘿，安迪，你能帮我再申请一次吗?
- It is, isn't it? - Hey, Andy, could you reapply for me?

578
00:34:55,428 --> 00:34:57,472
是的。是啊，我抓住你了，伙计。
Yeah. Yeah, I got you, bud.

579
00:34:58,181 --> 00:34:59,241
——谢谢。-告诉我什么时候。
- Thank you. - Tell me when.

580
00:34:59,265 --> 00:35:00,266
这很好。
That's good.

581
00:35:00,350 --> 00:35:01,351
——你好吗?——是的。
- You good? - Yes.

582
00:35:01,434 --> 00:35:03,436
-这不可能。-不，不是。
- This is impossible. - No, it isn't.

583
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:08,358
胡迪尼曾经说过:“我的大脑是让我获得自由的钥匙。”
Houdini once said, "My brain is the key that sets me free."

584
00:35:08,441 --> 00:35:09,693
胡迪尼爱尔兰吗?
Was Houdini Irish?

585
00:35:09,776 --> 00:35:11,629
不，他是匈牙利人。那是个坏印象。
No, he was Hungarian. That was a bad impression.

586
00:35:11,653 --> 00:35:16,658
好了，完全呼气，然后用这个放松的时间将手臂一直伸到后面。
Okay, exhale fully, then use that slack to reach your arm all the way back.

587
00:35:17,325 --> 00:35:19,119
喔!
Whoo.

588
00:35:19,202 --> 00:35:21,454
好吧!现在你明白了。高5。
All right! Now you're getting it. High five.

589
00:35:22,205 --> 00:35:23,415
当然可以。
Of course.

590
00:35:23,498 --> 00:35:25,667
——哦。-那是我的错。
- Ooh. - That is my bad.

591
00:35:26,209 --> 00:35:27,585
是的!
Yes!

592
00:35:27,669 --> 00:35:29,629
现在我可以和兔子们一起工作了吗?
Now do I get to work with the bunnies?

593
00:35:29,713 --> 00:35:32,507
露丝，你还没准备好做兔子呢。
Ruth, you are nowhere near bunny-ready.

594
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:34,884
你为什么要这样搅乱我的情绪?
Why are you messing with my emotions like this?

595
00:35:35,552 --> 00:35:38,430
在你跑之前，你得学会爬。
Well, before you run, you gotta learn how to crawl.

596
00:35:38,513 --> 00:35:42,100
这让我想到……海龟。
Which leads me to... the turtles.

597
00:35:42,183 --> 00:35:45,395
又小又慢，就像你们一样。来吧，拿一个。
Tiny and slow, just like you guys. Go ahead, grab one.

598
00:35:45,478 --> 00:35:48,481
兔子桩!我准备好拥抱了!
Bunny pile! I'm ready for my cuddles!

599
00:35:48,565 --> 00:35:50,316
到我这里来，我的朋友们!
Come to me, my friends!

600
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:51,526
得到他们!很快!
Get 'em! Quickly!

601
00:35:51,609 --> 00:35:53,111
露丝!不!
Ruth! No!

602
00:35:53,194 --> 00:35:54,529
-把乌龟扔了。——回来!
- Drop the turtles. - Come back!

603
00:35:54,612 --> 00:35:57,032
——不!他们得到了!-你要去哪里?
- No! They're getting out! - Where are you going?

604
00:35:57,115 --> 00:35:59,868
在盒子里。抓住一只兔子!每个人，每个人，快抓住他们。
In the box. Grab a bunny! Everybody, everybody, just get 'em.

605
00:35:59,951 --> 00:36:01,661
-你要去哪里?-去拿兔子!
- Where are you going? - Get the bunnies!

606
00:36:01,745 --> 00:36:05,540
呼气放松。把你的胳膊举过肩膀。
Exhale to create some slack. Get your arm up over your shoulder.

607
00:36:05,623 --> 00:36:06,958
让他们离水远点!
Keep 'em away from the water!

608
00:36:07,042 --> 00:36:10,003
在那里!
Over there!

609
00:36:10,086 --> 00:36:11,087
人失望!
Man down!

610
00:36:11,796 --> 00:36:14,674
好吧，这是一个我们不用担心大礼帽的小屋。
Well, that's one cabin we don't have to worry about for Top Hat.

611
00:36:15,842 --> 00:36:18,011
维克，我怎么跟你说的?是一个好去处。
Vic, what did I tell you? Be nice.

612
00:36:19,971 --> 00:36:21,222
停止那些兔子!
Stop those bunnies!

613
00:36:21,306 --> 00:36:23,641
——电子战。恶心。——得到他们!
- Ew. Gross. - Get 'em!

614
00:36:23,725 --> 00:36:25,602
——在那里!-是啊，我刚才尖叫了。
- Over there! - Yeah, I just screamed that.

615
00:36:26,186 --> 00:36:28,688
-注意你的紧身衣。-他们要跑了!
- Concentrate on your straitjackets. - They're getting away!

616
00:36:28,772 --> 00:36:31,066
——詹妮尔在哪?——可怜的。抓兔子。
- Where's Janelle? - Pathetic. Grab the bunny.

617
00:36:31,149 --> 00:36:33,610
你为什么要逃避我?
Why are you running from me?

618
00:36:34,027 --> 00:36:35,111
我有一个!
I got one!

619
00:36:35,612 --> 00:36:37,614
——等待。不,我没有……-在灌木丛下面!
- Wait. No, I didn't... - Under the bush!

620
00:36:38,698 --> 00:36:39,866
明白了!
Gotcha!

621
00:36:40,450 --> 00:36:41,868
不,不要!
No, don't go!

622
00:36:41,951 --> 00:36:44,371
我只是在找跑掉的兔子。
I'm just looking for the bunnies that got away.

623
00:36:44,829 --> 00:36:47,207
-我看起来像兔子吗?——什么?不。
- Do I look like a bunny? - What? No.

624
00:36:47,749 --> 00:36:51,419
嗯，可能有一点。我是说，像兔子一样可爱。
Well, maybe a little. I mean, like, cute like a bunny.

625
00:36:51,503 --> 00:36:54,839
嗯,不是cute-cute。并不是说你不可爱。
Well, not cute-cute. Not that you're not cute.

626
00:36:54,923 --> 00:36:58,927
他不肯骗受害人，所以我把他的手机塞进了一大口。
He wouldn't trick the Vic, so I palmed his phone into a Big Gulp.

627
00:36:59,010 --> 00:37:02,889
你是怎么弄到钻石的?你看起来不错。
How'd you get with the Diamonds anyway? You seem nice.

628
00:37:02,972 --> 00:37:05,767
我父母可能为我和黑木乐队在一起付了额外的钱。
My parents probably paid extra for me to be with Darkwood.

629
00:37:05,850 --> 00:37:07,227
他们真是太酷了。
That's pretty cool of them.

630
00:37:07,310 --> 00:37:09,187
他们并不是想耍酷。
They're not trying to be cool.

631
00:37:09,270 --> 00:37:12,524
