I don't know. It's just fun.

636
00:37:25,412 --> 00:37:27,831
就像你对你的身体做的拼图，我猜。
Like a puzzle you do with your body, I guess.

637
00:37:29,332 --> 00:37:31,751
好了，现在我真的得走了。
Okay, now I really gotta go.

638
00:37:31,835 --> 00:37:33,878
顺便说一下，我叫詹妮尔。
I'm Janelle, by the way.

639
00:37:34,713 --> 00:37:35,714
西奥。
Theo.

640
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:41,302
离高顶礼帽还有17天。
Seventeen days until Top Hat.

641
00:37:41,386 --> 00:37:43,013
午餐是砂锅菜。
Lunch will be casserole.

642
00:37:43,096 --> 00:37:44,806
目前还不清楚是哪种类型。
It is unclear what kind.

643
00:37:44,889 --> 00:37:48,560
这就是我们所说的法式降酒。你看到了什么?
This is what we call the French drop. You see?

644
00:37:48,643 --> 00:37:51,563
你得保护角度不让观众看到。
You got to protect the angle from the audience.

645
00:37:51,646 --> 00:37:53,126
——噢,噢。-好吧，你们试试看。
- Ooh, ooh. - All right, you guys try.

646
00:37:55,859 --> 00:37:58,153
令人惊讶的是，这并不可怕，露丝。
That was surprisingly not terrible, Ruth.

647
00:37:58,236 --> 00:37:59,446
谢谢你,安迪。
Thanks, Andy.

648
00:38:05,577 --> 00:38:06,870
干得好,安迪。
Attaboy, Andy.

649
00:38:06,953 --> 00:38:11,082
看来你们一直在听我精彩的教学。
Seems like you guys have been listening to my amazing teaching after all.

650
00:38:11,166 --> 00:38:13,710
魔术并不是一种有氧运动。
Magic isn't exactly a cardio workout.

651
00:38:13,793 --> 00:38:17,714
你的父母坚持让你在这个夏天进行体育锻炼
Your parents are insisting we try to get you some physical activity this summer,

652
00:38:17,797 --> 00:38:18,965
所以…看起来有生机。
so... look alive.

653
00:38:24,012 --> 00:38:26,514
好的,锻炼结束了!回到魔法!
Okay, workout over! Back to magic!

654
00:38:26,598 --> 00:38:30,810
消失……和外观!
Vanish... and appearance!

655
00:38:31,811 --> 00:38:33,730
哇。好工作。
Wow. Good job.

656
00:38:34,814 --> 00:38:38,526
好吧，我想我们该进入下一个阶段了。
Okay, I think it's time we take things to the next level.

657
00:38:38,610 --> 00:38:39,652
哇!
Whoa!

658
00:38:39,736 --> 00:38:42,989
什么?我说我想和兔子一起工作，
What? I said I wanted to work with bunnies,

659
00:38:43,073 --> 00:38:45,992
不是那些可怕的，会飞的便便机。
not those terrifying, flying poop-machines.

660
00:38:46,076 --> 00:38:48,536
鲁斯，你解放了所有的兔子，
Well, Ruth, you liberated all of the bunnies,

661
00:38:48,620 --> 00:38:51,373
这就是我们要解决的问题。
so this is what we have to work with.

662
00:38:51,456 --> 00:38:52,874
举起你的手指。
Raise out your finger.

663
00:38:54,125 --> 00:38:56,461
鸽子就像会飞的兔子。
Doves are like flying bunnies.

664
00:38:56,544 --> 00:38:59,172
它们是魔术师情感的延伸。
They're an extension of a magician's emotions.

665
00:38:59,255 --> 00:39:02,050
如果你自信，那就是自信。如果你紧张……
If you're confident, it's confident. If you're nervous...

666
00:39:02,133 --> 00:39:03,593
哇!
Whoa!

667
00:39:05,136 --> 00:39:06,596
然后发生的事情。
Then that happens.

668
00:39:11,476 --> 00:39:13,019
很明显，这也是事实。
And apparently so does that.

669
00:39:13,103 --> 00:39:14,270
好的,心。
Okay, Hearts.

670
00:39:14,354 --> 00:39:20,151
我想你已经准备好聆听魔术界最大的秘密之一了。
I think you're ready to hear one of the biggest secrets in all of magic.

671
00:39:20,235 --> 00:39:23,655
每个伟大魔术师的背后，都有……
Behind every great magician, there is...

672
00:39:23,738 --> 00:39:25,907
一个更好的裁缝。
An even better tailor.

673
00:39:27,492 --> 00:39:30,412
——好。那件运动外套真棒。
- Nice. - That sports coat is amazing.

674
00:39:30,870 --> 00:39:35,000
贾德，我感觉到人们对服装的热情了吗?
Judd, am I sensing an enthusiasm for costumes?

675
00:39:38,128 --> 00:39:42,716
欢迎来到服装设计的奇妙世界。
Welcome to the fabulous world of costume design.

676
00:39:45,010 --> 00:39:48,304
如果你不介意的话，我想今天剩下的时间我还是在这里度过吧。
Think I'm gonna spend the rest of the day here, if that's cool with you.

677
00:39:48,805 --> 00:39:50,974
露丝，也许你需要大点的。
Ruth, maybe you just need something bigger.

678
00:39:53,518 --> 00:39:55,395
伊森，她不是食物，好吗?
Now, Ethan, she's not food, okay?

679
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:05,447
哇。
Whoa.

680
00:40:06,239 --> 00:40:08,700
鹰现在是我的最爱了。
Hawks are my thing now.

681
00:40:08,783 --> 00:40:12,078
鸟儿喜欢绿色。这就像……你就像一棵树。
Birds love the color green. It's like... It's like you're a tree.

682
00:40:16,750 --> 00:40:18,418
好吧，跟我来。
All right, come with me.

683
00:40:21,755 --> 00:40:23,715
嗨,爸爸。我有一个新把戏。
Hey, Dad. I got a new trick.

684
00:40:23,798 --> 00:40:26,176
我现在不行，西奥。我赶不上飞机了。
I-I can't right now, Theo. I'm late for my flight.

685
00:40:26,259 --> 00:40:29,512
-为你妈妈做。-妈妈不喜欢魔法。好吗?
- Do it for your mom. - Mom's not into magic. Please?

686
00:40:30,263 --> 00:40:32,974
-是的。好吧。好吧。——好的。
- Yeah. Okay. Okay. - All right.

687
00:40:33,058 --> 00:40:34,476
选择一个卡。
Pick a card.

688
00:40:34,934 --> 00:40:35,935
好了。
There we go.

689
00:40:36,019 --> 00:40:38,730
好吧。别让我看这是红桃j。
All right. Now don't let me see it's the jack of hearts.

690
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:42,067
好吧。
Okay.

691
00:40:42,150 --> 00:40:43,777
这很好。你怎么知道的?
That's pretty good. How'd you know?

692
00:40:43,860 --> 00:40:45,862
因为那是我。我是红心j。
'Cause that's me. I'm the jack of hearts.

693
00:40:45,945 --> 00:40:49,407
和…这是你的。
And... that's you.

694
00:40:50,575 --> 00:40:53,161
-你是红心之王。-你是怎么做到的…
- You're the king of hearts. - How did you do...

695
00:40:53,244 --> 00:40:55,163
这是难以置信的。你是不可思议的,西奥。
That's incredible. You're incredible, Theo.

696
00:40:55,246 --> 00:40:57,499
西奥。西奥。
Theo. Theo.

697
00:40:57,582 --> 00:41:01,169
听着，每个人的行为都在成形，但我们都还没有。
Look, everyone's acts are shaping up, but neither of us have one yet.

698
00:41:01,628 --> 00:41:04,839
所以我想我们可以组成一个魔术喜剧二人组
So I was thinking we could form a magical comedy duo

699
00:41:04,923 --> 00:41:09,135
与我做勇敢的玩笑，而你wow每个人与你的卡魔术。
with me doing plucky banter while you wow everyone with your card magic.

700
00:41:09,219 --> 00:41:12,472
我读到过放屁的声音很能取悦大众。
I've read that fart sounds are quite the crowd-pleaser.

701
00:41:12,555 --> 00:41:16,643
你再偷偷给我一点奶酪，我就把这个地方的屋顶炸飞。
You sneak me even a bit of cheese, and I will blow the roof off this place.

702
00:41:16,726 --> 00:41:19,562
-内特，千万别在人群上放屁——好的。
- Nate, definitely don't fart on the crowd. - Okay.

703
00:41:19,646 --> 00:41:22,023
你们为什么不工作?演出在下周举行。
Why aren't you guys working? The show's next week.

704
00:41:22,107 --> 00:41:24,109
我还在努力学习我的专业。
I'm still trying to figure out my specialty.

705
00:41:24,192 --> 00:41:26,736
是的，这是个棘手的问题。
Yeah, that is a tricky one.

706
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:29,322
内特，这个电影院有几张票?
Hey, Nate, how many seats are in this theater?

707
00:41:30,365 --> 00:41:31,991
273. 为什么?
273. Why?

708
00:41:32,075 --> 00:41:34,869
为什么?因为你这么快就能做到。
Why? Because it's freakish how quickly you could do that.

709
00:41:34,953 --> 00:41:37,038
你有别人没有的特别的东西。
You've got something special that no one else has.

710
00:41:37,622 --> 00:41:41,543
突出的尾骨实际上比你想象的更常见。
A protruding tailbone is actually more common than you'd expect.

711
00:41:41,626 --> 00:41:43,688
他说的是你计算东西的方式。
He's talking about the way you do your counting stuff.

712
00:41:43,712 --> 00:41:48,133
是的，我只是数。我数，组，乘，还有…
Yeah, I just count. I count and group and multiply and...

713
00:41:48,216 --> 00:41:49,718
这是魔法。
That's magic.

714
00:41:49,801 --> 00:41:53,722
你的大脑就像一个巨大的、怪异的魔法计算器。
Your brain is like a big, weird magic calculator.

715
00:41:53,805 --> 00:41:56,057
你可能是个唯心论者。
You could be a mentalist.

716
00:41:56,141 --> 00:41:57,392
喜欢用黑木制作克里斯吗?
Like Kris Darkwood?

717
00:41:57,475 --> 00:41:59,644
比克里斯·多克伍德还好。
Better than Kris Dorkwood.

718
00:42:00,145 --> 00:42:02,355
-我需要坐下来——你。
- I need to sit down. - You are.

719
00:42:13,324 --> 00:42:14,659
很好。
Very nice.

720
00:42:15,910 --> 00:42:17,871
看上去不错,伙计们。哇!
Looking good, guys. Whoo!

721
00:42:17,954 --> 00:42:19,956
-安迪，过来。——好的。
- Andy, come here. - Okay.

722
00:42:21,875 --> 00:42:22,959
哇。
Whoa.

723
00:42:24,294 --> 00:42:25,295
是的。
Yep.

724
00:42:26,379 --> 00:42:28,673
——好。是的!-看起来不错。
- Good. Yes! - That looked so good.

725
00:42:29,591 --> 00:42:31,676
西奥，让我们看看你的本事。
Okay, Theo, show us what you got.

726
00:42:38,308 --> 00:42:41,644
——难以置信。-好吧，我们休息十分钟。
- Unbelievable. - Okay, let's take ten.

727
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:44,481
伙计们，继续练习你的小指。
You guys, keep working on your pinky break.

728
00:42:44,564 --> 00:42:46,358
内森，让你的小指休息一下。
Nathan, give your pinky a break.

729
00:42:46,983 --> 00:42:50,320
-那是痒，不是刺。我发誓。-好吧，很好。
- It was an itch, not a pick. I swear. - Okay, yeah, cool, all right.

730
00:42:50,403 --> 00:42:52,739
伙计，怎么回事?你还在你的脑子里。
Dude, what's going on? You're still in your head.

731
00:42:53,198 --> 00:42:55,468
你知道吗?跟我来。有些东西你需要看。
You know what? Follow me. There's something you need to see.

732
00:42:55,492 --> 00:42:56,743
来吧。
Come on.

733
00:43:01,873 --> 00:43:03,667
普雷斯顿的秘密图书馆。
Preston's secret library.

734
00:43:04,501 --> 00:43:06,628
当我像你这么大的时候，他把我带到这里。
He took me here when I was about your age.

735
00:43:06,711 --> 00:43:09,964
他说只有真正杰出的魔术师才能参加。
He said it was for only truly exceptional magicians.

736
00:43:10,799 --> 00:43:12,425
去看看吧。
Go ahead, check it out.

737
00:43:28,024 --> 00:43:29,526
这是一个猫头鹰。
It's an owl.

738
00:43:33,905 --> 00:43:35,448
是你和黑木吗?
Is that you and Darkwood?

739
00:43:36,199 --> 00:43:38,201
哇。
Wow.

740
00:43:38,827 --> 00:43:39,828
是的。
Yep.

741
00:43:40,662 --> 00:43:43,623
-对，就是我们。——“Abraca-Duo”?
- Yeah, that's us. - The "Abraca-Duo"?

742
00:43:43,707 --> 00:43:47,210
嘿,别法官。这在当时是一个非常容易记住的名字。
Hey, don't judge. It was a very catchy name at the time.

743
00:43:48,086 --> 00:43:50,088
那么，你们现在为什么讨厌对方呢?
So, why do you hate each other now?

744
00:43:52,966 --> 00:43:54,217
哇。嗯…
Wow. Um...

745
00:43:55,093 --> 00:43:57,053
当我们还是露营者的时候，我们很亲密。
When we were campers, we were close.

746
00:43:57,137 --> 00:43:58,763
我对你下了咒语
♪ I put a spell on you ♪

747
00:43:58,847 --> 00:44:00,098
我很酷…
I was like the cool...

748
00:44:00,181 --> 00:44:01,683
训练营的老巨星
older superstar of the camp

749
00:44:01,766 --> 00:44:04,060
她是我的门生。
and she was kinda my protégée.

750
00:44:05,061 --> 00:44:07,480
因为你是我的
♪ Because you're mine ♪

751
00:44:09,607 --> 00:44:11,526
放学后，我们成了伙伴。
After school, we became partners.

752
00:44:11,609 --> 00:44:13,737
一开始，我们只是做了很多街头魔术。
At first, we just did a lot of street magic.

753
00:44:13,820 --> 00:44:15,321
停止你所做的事情
♪ Stop the things you do ♪

754
00:44:15,405 --> 00:44:18,950
但是消息传开了，很快我们就预订了真正的演出。
But word got around and pretty soon we were booking real gigs.

755
00:44:19,951 --> 00:44:22,871
我不是吹牛，但我们在一起真的很棒。
Not to brag, but we were pretty amazing together.

756
00:44:26,041 --> 00:44:29,586
我知道这有点难以置信，但我们确实曾经是一对。
I know it's kinda hard to believe, but we actually used to be a couple.

757
00:44:29,669 --> 00:44:31,713
很明显。
It's obvious.

758
00:44:33,423 --> 00:44:36,926
我是说，你看得出她对你还有感觉。
I mean, you can tell she still has feelings for you.

759
00:44:37,010 --> 00:44:38,470
-我知道，对吧?-是的。
- I know, right? - Yeah.

760
00:44:38,553 --> 00:44:40,680
就像，忘记它，你知道吗?
It's like, get over it, you know?

761
00:44:42,140 --> 00:44:46,061
不管怎样，我们开始制作越来越大的影院，
Anyway, we started doing bigger and bigger theaters,

762
00:44:46,144 --> 00:44:47,937
想在维加斯有自己的演出
trying to get our own show in Vegas.

763
00:44:48,813 --> 00:44:52,275
然后她背着我走了。
Then she went behind my back.

764
00:44:52,359 --> 00:44:54,736
没带我去见一个大电视制作人。
Took a meeting with a big TV booker without me.

765
00:44:55,320 --> 00:44:59,282
我发现后，我们大吵了一架，然后分手了。
When I found out, we got in this huge fight and we broke up.

766
00:44:59,657 --> 00:45:03,370
她做了电视独唱，一夜成名。
She did the solo TV gig and skyrocketed to fame.

767
00:45:04,287 --> 00:45:07,374
我也开始独奏，但是…
I also started to perform solo, but...

768
00:45:10,251 --> 00:45:13,755
这是粗糙的。
It was rough.

769
00:45:14,756 --> 00:45:18,051
一天晚上，我只为一个人做了一个节目……托尼。
One night I did a show for just one person... Tony.

770
00:45:18,677 --> 00:45:20,261
那天早些时候他修理了我的车。
He worked on my car earlier that day.

771
00:45:20,345 --> 00:45:22,889
你能想象为一个人施魔法吗?
Can you imagine just doing magic for one person?

772
00:45:22,972 --> 00:45:27,185
我能。这就是我施魔法的原因。为我的爸爸。
I can. That's why I did magic. For my dad.

773
00:45:29,521 --> 00:45:31,189
我只会为他表演。
I'd only perform for him.

774
00:45:31,940 --> 00:45:34,025
但现在，他…
But now, he's, um...

775
00:45:36,986 --> 00:45:38,697
——他……-嘿，没事的。
- He... - Hey, it's okay.

776
00:45:40,281 --> 00:45:42,200
我们现在不需要谈这个。
We don't have to talk about that now.

777
00:45:42,659 --> 00:45:44,494
快点，我们离开这里。
Come on, let's get out of here.

778
00:45:54,963 --> 00:45:56,881
——要去哪里吗?-让我出去。
- Going somewhere? - Let me out.

779
00:45:57,382 --> 00:46:01,261
你整个夏天都在练习，在练习前偷偷溜走。
You've been pulling this all summer, sneaking away before practice.

780
00:46:01,344 --> 00:46:03,471
你知道是你自己选择来的吗?
You know you chose to come here?

781
00:46:03,555 --> 00:46:05,974
不是真的。我从来没施过魔法。
Not really. I've never even done magic before.

782
00:46:06,057 --> 00:46:08,727
-我父母刚把我送走。——我很抱歉。
- My parents just sent me away. - I'm sorry.

783
00:46:08,810 --> 00:46:10,270
那真的不公平。
That's really not fair.

784
00:46:10,353 --> 00:46:12,230
好吧，你懂的。放我出去。
Okay, you get it. So let me out.

785
00:46:12,313 --> 00:46:13,732
可以这样做。
Could do that.

786
00:46:13,815 --> 00:46:17,152
但如果你选择把整个夏天看作是一种挑战呢?
But what if you chose to look at this whole summer as a kind of challenge?

787
00:46:17,235 --> 00:46:19,738
就像绑着这张网的蟒蛇一样。
Like that constrictor knot holding this net.

788
00:46:19,821 --> 00:46:20,822
你是什么意思?
What do you mean?

789
00:46:20,905 --> 00:46:24,159
你被困在这里了，就像你被困在这张网里一样。
Well, you're stuck here at camp, just like you're stuck in this net.

790
00:46:24,242 --> 00:46:27,120
你没有选择任何一种情况，但它们确实发生了。
You didn't choose either situation, but they happened.

791
00:46:27,579 --> 00:46:28,788
所以，你有两个选择。
So, you have two options.

792
