And for my next trick,

964
00:57:00,003 --> 00:57:03,798
我给大家下了个咒语，让大家不再伤心
I put a spell on all of us to quit being sad

965
00:57:03,882 --> 00:57:06,593
祝你度过最美好的夜晚。
and have the best night ever.

966
00:57:09,054 --> 00:57:11,890
