967
00:57:11,973 --> 00:57:12,974
真的吗?
Really?

968
00:57:13,058 --> 00:57:16,019
你觉得是关于什么的?你觉得她的棉花糖用完了?
What do you think it's about? You think she ran out of marshmallows?

969
00:57:16,102 --> 00:57:19,939
她可能把棉花糖用完了。詹妮尔，我们有棉花糖!
She probably ran out of marshmallows. Hey, Janelle, we have marshmallows!

970
00:57:20,023 --> 00:57:21,358
-冷静，冷静!——为什么?
- Chill out, chill out! - Why?

971
00:57:21,441 --> 00:57:24,611
女士们会喜欢你的。
Ooh, lady's gonna like you.

972
00:57:24,694 --> 00:57:27,447
——K-I-S-S-I-N-G。——西奥!
- K-I-S-S-I-N-G. - Theo!

973
00:57:27,530 --> 00:57:31,659
西奥喜欢詹妮尔。西奥喜欢詹妮尔。
Theo likes Janelle. Theo likes Janelle.

974
00:57:40,585 --> 00:57:43,814
你打算什么时候把你是专业魔术师的事实说出来?
When were you gonna come clean about the fact that you're a professional magician?

975
00:57:43,838 --> 00:57:44,839
我不是。
I'm not.

976
00:57:45,757 --> 00:57:48,927
-我看见你和维克在一起这是疯狂的。——谢谢。
