977
00:57:49,010 --> 00:57:51,680
是啊，你可能在这神奇的事情上发现了一些东西。
Yeah, you might be onto something with this whole magic thing.

978
00:57:51,763 --> 00:57:53,181
很有趣,对吧?
It's fun, right?

979
00:57:54,849 --> 00:57:56,267
这是有趣的。
This is fun.

980
00:58:03,149 --> 00:58:04,401
每个人都冻结。
Everyone freeze.

981
00:58:07,862 --> 00:58:09,739
露丝，你在做什么?
Ruth, what are you doing?

982
00:58:09,823 --> 00:58:10,990
待回来。
Stay back.

983
00:58:11,074 --> 00:58:13,326
我整个夏天都在为这一刻而训练。
I've been training for this moment all summer.

984
00:58:14,786 --> 00:58:17,997
伙计们，我想那是弗雷德。它一定是从笼子里跑出来的。
Guys, I think that's Fred. He must've gotten out of his cage.

985
00:58:18,081 --> 00:58:21,167
感谢上帝。弗雷德的臭腺被切除了。
Thank God. Fred had his stink glands removed.

986
00:58:21,584 --> 00:58:23,461
但我们还是要带他回去。
But we still need to guide him back.

987
00:58:24,629 --> 00:58:26,506
不要听他们的。
Don't listen to them.

988
00:58:26,589 --> 00:58:27,966
不要看他们。
Don't look at them.

989
00:58:28,925 --> 00:58:31,928
只有你和我。
It's just you and me.

990
00:58:36,266 --> 00:58:38,143
这些看起来不像弗雷德的条纹。
Those don't look like Fred's stripes.

991
00:58:38,226 --> 00:58:40,228
不。我mustelid过敏。
No. My mustelid allergy.

992
00:58:40,311 --> 00:58:42,731
内森,持有它。这不是弗雷德。这不是弗雷德!
Nathan, hold it. It's not Fred. It's not Fred!

993
00:58:56,828 --> 00:58:59,706
我这么做是出于爱。
I'm doing this out of love.

994
00:59:03,877 --> 00:59:07,088
别担心。我有一个给你!
Don't worry. I got one for you!

995
00:59:08,923 --> 00:59:10,300
Sker-ploosh !
Sker-ploosh!

996
00:59:28,234 --> 00:59:29,361
不!别碰我。
No! Don't touch me.

997
00:59:39,746 --> 00:59:40,747
明确的。
Clear.

998
00:59:43,958 --> 00:59:44,958
嘘。
Shh.

999
00:59:50,173 --> 00:59:52,050
早上好,露营者。
Good morning, campers.

1000
00:59:52,133 --> 00:59:53,885
还有两天就要戴大礼帽了
Two days until Top Hat,

1001
00:59:53,968 --> 00:59:56,971
我很兴奋，我今天可以吃午饭了，
and I am so excited I may actually eat our lunch today,

1002
00:59:57,055 --> 00:59:59,224
那将是肉糕，也将是晚餐。
which will be meat loaf, as will be dinner.

1003
00:59:59,307 --> 01:00:02,268
事实上，这个夏天剩下的时间，我们只需要和肉卷一起吃。
In fact, we're just gonna roll with meat loaf for the rest of the summer.

1004
01:00:05,188 --> 01:00:07,190
安迪,救命!
Andy, help!

1005
01:00:08,983 --> 01:00:10,568
他们也抓住了我。
They got me too.

1006
01:00:13,071 --> 01:00:15,073
的帮助!
Help!

1007
01:00:17,492 --> 01:00:20,620
嘿，怎么回事?把这些带回来。
Hey, what's going on? Bring those back.

1008
01:00:20,704 --> 01:00:21,705
穿过。
Coming through.

1009
01:00:21,788 --> 01:00:24,028
他们为最后的演出检查了一切。
They've checked everything out for the final performance.

1010
01:00:24,416 --> 01:00:28,169
你对老鹰伊森做了什么?伊桑·霍克是我的全部。
What are you doing with Ethan the hawk? Ethan Hawk is my whole act.

1011
01:00:28,962 --> 01:00:30,880
你不睡，你就输了，小家伙。
You snooze, you lose, little one.

1012
01:00:32,132 --> 01:00:34,718
一切都在哪儿?他们弄乱了我的东西。
Where's everything? They're messing with my things.

1013
01:00:35,802 --> 01:00:37,262
那么,什么是…我的表。
So, what is... My table.

1014
01:00:37,345 --> 01:00:39,639
没有什么。没有球，没有牌。
There's nothing. There's no balls, no cards.

1015
01:00:40,724 --> 01:00:43,309
-钻石队检查了所有的道具。——什么?
- The Diamonds checked out all the props. - What?

1016
01:00:44,269 --> 01:00:45,645
-真不敢相信。——什么?
- I don't believe this. - What?

1017
01:00:47,647 --> 01:00:50,442
-他们使我们的心变小了。-怎么会这样?
- They shrunk our hearts. - How'd that happen?

1018
01:00:50,525 --> 01:00:52,861
他们把烘干机的设置调到了“重型”。
They switched the dryer setting to "heavy duty."

1019
01:00:52,944 --> 01:00:54,904
混合运动服装不是“重型”。
Polyblend athletic wear is not "heavy duty."

1020
01:00:54,988 --> 01:00:57,049
你觉得你是不是放错位置了?
Do you think maybe you just put it on the wrong setting?

1021
01:00:57,073 --> 01:00:59,176
你是…你是在指责我洗衣服的错误吗?
Are you... Are you accusing me of making a laundry mistake?

1022
01:00:59,200 --> 01:01:03,455
我洗衣服从不出错，先生。我创造了洗衣奇迹。
I do not make laundry mistakes, sir. I make laundry miracles.

1023
01:01:03,538 --> 01:01:05,081
钻石毁了我们的行为。
The Diamonds have ruined our act.

1024
01:01:05,165 --> 01:01:06,875
我们还有计数轮。
We still have the counting wheel.

1025
01:01:09,794 --> 01:01:11,129
他们毁了一切!
They ruined everything!

1026
01:01:11,212 --> 01:01:14,174
关于黑木镇的事你是对的。她是冷血动物。
You were right about Darkwood. She is cold-blooded.

1027
01:01:14,257 --> 01:01:17,052
我们不可能为最后的演出及时准备好新材料。
We'll never get new stuff together in time for the final performance.

1028
01:01:17,135 --> 01:01:20,555
面对现实吧，伙计们，都结束了。他们击败了我们。
Face it, guys, it's over. They beat us.

1029
01:01:20,638 --> 01:01:22,533
反正我们也没有真正的机会。
It's not like we ever really had a chance anyway.

1030
01:01:22,557 --> 01:01:26,728
那不是真的。还记得你们刚来的时候有多可怕吗?
That's not true. Remember how horrible you guys were when you first got here?

1031
01:01:26,811 --> 01:01:28,688
你们现在少多了。
You guys suck way less now.

1032
01:01:28,772 --> 01:01:31,399
-多谢了-你是在恭维我吗?
- Thanks a lot. - Was that supposed to be a compliment?

1033
01:01:31,483 --> 01:01:33,151
说真的，我们不能放弃。
Seriously, we can't quit.

1034
01:01:33,234 --> 01:01:36,112
因为当事情变得困难时，心脏就会跳动起来。
'Cause when the going gets hard, the Hearts get going.

1035
01:01:36,196 --> 01:01:38,365
那很好。你刚想出来的?
That was pretty good. You just came up with that?

1036
01:01:38,448 --> 01:01:40,950
-很好，不是吗?-是的。这是可怕的。
- That was good, wasn't it? - Yeah. That was awesome.

1037
01:01:41,034 --> 01:01:44,204
你知道吗?我想我知道我们需要什么了。
You know what? I think I know what we need.

1038
01:01:44,287 --> 01:01:45,705
跟我来。
Follow me.

1039
01:01:53,129 --> 01:01:54,839
好的,帮派。
Okay, gang.

1040
01:01:54,923 --> 01:01:58,426
我们到了。
And here we are.

1041
01:01:59,135 --> 01:02:00,428
好吧。
Okay.

1042
01:02:05,600 --> 01:02:07,018
哇!
Whoa!

1043
01:02:07,102 --> 01:02:09,437
你是怎么做到的?磁铁或电线吗?
How'd you do that? Magnets or wires?

1044
01:02:09,521 --> 01:02:11,981
既不。现代科技。
Neither. Just modern technology.

1045
01:02:12,065 --> 01:02:13,692
那么，我们在这里做什么?
So, what are we doing here?

1046
01:02:13,775 --> 01:02:15,902
一天晚上，我在堪萨斯城演出，
One night, I was playing a show in Kansas City,

1047
01:02:15,985 --> 01:02:18,154
航空公司把我的机箱放错飞机了。
and the airline put my prop case on the wrong plane.

1048
01:02:18,238 --> 01:02:19,364
哦,不太好。
Ooh, not good.

1049
01:02:19,447 --> 01:02:23,702
我只好在机场的便利店里随便找些东西凑合着用。
I had to improvise with whatever I could find at the airport convenience store.

1050
01:02:23,785 --> 01:02:26,538
而这正是我现在要求你们做的。
And that is exactly what I'm challenging you guys to do right now.

1051
01:02:26,621 --> 01:02:28,248
谁说我们需要道具?
Who says we need props?

1052
01:02:28,331 --> 01:02:30,750
戏法是魔术师创造的，而不是魔术师创造的。
Magicians create the trick, not the other way around.

1053
01:02:30,834 --> 01:02:33,294
你可以把它想象成一个神奇的寻宝活动。
Think of it as like a magical treasure hunt.

1054
01:02:33,378 --> 01:02:35,922
通常在寻宝游戏中，参与者会被提供
Um, typically in a treasure hunt, the participants are provided

1055
01:02:36,006 --> 01:02:37,424
有线索，有地图，有传说…
with clues, a map, or a legend...

1056
01:02:37,507 --> 01:02:39,944
——走吧。30分钟后见。-我们会得到线索还是地图?
- Let's go. See you in 30 minutes. - Are we gonna get clues or a map?

1057
01:02:39,968 --> 01:02:43,054
玩得开心。想想看，好吗?即兴发挥。
Have fun. Figure it out, all right? Improvise.

1058
01:03:01,114 --> 01:03:02,615
也许这一个。
Maybe this one.

1059
01:03:04,325 --> 01:03:06,661
这是垃圾。这不是形状。
This is garbage. This is just not the shape.

1060
01:03:07,996 --> 01:03:09,998
那
That.

1061
01:03:17,839 --> 01:03:19,174
内森,内森。
Nathan, Nathan.

1062
01:03:21,926 --> 01:03:24,596
对不起,每一个人。我能引起你的注意吗?
Excuse me, everybody. Can I get your attention?

1063
01:03:24,679 --> 01:03:26,890
今天，我们将向你展示一些魔术。
Today, we're gonna show you some magic.

1064
01:03:27,474 --> 01:03:29,017
把它拿走，维拉。
Take it away, Vera.

1065
01:03:36,483 --> 01:03:37,484
太酷了。
So cool.

1066
01:03:42,530 --> 01:03:43,531
——明白了吗?-是的。
- Got it? - Yeah.

1067
01:03:43,615 --> 01:03:44,616
酷。
Cool.

1068
01:03:46,826 --> 01:03:48,995
对不起，这个刻度有多精确?
Excuse me, how accurate is that scale?

1069
01:03:49,079 --> 01:03:51,790
测量重量到千分之一磅。
Measures weight down to a thousandth of a pound.

1070
01:03:52,165 --> 01:03:55,418
如果他能猜出确切的重量，我们能免费得到这个糖果吗?
If he can guess the exact weight, can we have this candy for free?

1071
01:03:55,794 --> 01:03:57,796
确定。这是不可能的。
Sure. That's impossible.

1072
01:03:57,879 --> 01:04:02,092
这是不可能的，还是2.173磅?
Is it impossible, or is it 2.173 pounds?

1073
01:04:03,134 --> 01:04:05,720
2.173磅。
2.173 pounds.

1074
01:04:05,804 --> 01:04:07,555
——是的!——这是不可思议的。
- Yeah! - That's incredible.

1075
01:04:07,639 --> 01:04:12,185
酷,伙计。我们省了11.54美元(含税)。
Cool, dude. We just saved $11.54, tax included.

1076
01:04:12,268 --> 01:04:13,645
哇!
Whoo!

1077
01:04:13,728 --> 01:04:15,480
我正试着学习如何正确持球。
I'm trying to learn to hold the ball right.

1078
01:04:15,563 --> 01:04:17,774
这些神奇的孩子们怎么了?
What's up with all these weird magic kids?

1079
01:04:17,857 --> 01:04:19,526
群lame-os。
Bunch of lame-os.

1080
01:04:19,609 --> 01:04:23,113
嘿!你说的那些是我的朋友。
Hey! Those are my friends you're talking about.

1081
01:04:23,196 --> 01:04:26,032
怪异让我们很棒。
And weird is what makes us awesome.

1082
01:04:26,116 --> 01:04:28,743
攻击!抓住他们的眼睛。
Attack! Go for their eyes.

1083
01:04:28,827 --> 01:04:31,621
走,走!
Go, go!

1084
01:04:35,667 --> 01:04:37,335
我还会碰一只兔子吗?
Am I ever going to touch a bunny?

1085
01:04:37,419 --> 01:04:39,879
总有一天，我保证你会的。
One day, I promise you will.

1086
01:04:40,380 --> 01:04:43,758
不是只有一打逃跑了吗?现在他们无处不在。
Didn't only a dozen escape? Now they're everywhere.

1087
01:04:43,842 --> 01:04:45,552
它们是如何繁殖的?
How are they multiplying?

1088
01:04:47,262 --> 01:04:50,098
我会让你父母解释的。
You know, I'm gonna let your parents explain that one.

1089
01:04:52,892 --> 01:04:57,022
好吧，已经超过你的宵禁时间了。进去睡觉吧。
Okay, way past your curfew. Get in there and get to bed.

1090
01:04:57,105 --> 01:04:59,232
你要去哪里?
Where are you going?

1091
01:04:59,315 --> 01:05:01,252
-我有账要算。-我保证他会来的
- I've got a score to settle. - I promise you he'll show.

1092
01:05:01,276 --> 01:05:03,069
用黑木制作嘿,!
Hey, Darkwood!

1093
01:05:03,153 --> 01:05:05,131
他现在就在那里。好吧。我待会再打给你。
There he is right now. All right. I'll talk to you later.

1094
01:05:05,155 --> 01:05:06,823
把电话挂了，你这个怪物。
Get off the phone, you monster.

1095
01:05:07,699 --> 01:05:09,701
你刚才叫我怪物吗?
Did you just call me a monster?

1096
01:05:09,784 --> 01:05:13,455
破坏我和我的事业是一回事，但是孩子呢?
It's one thing to sabotage me and my career, but children?

1097
01:05:13,538 --> 01:05:15,790
你真的能接受这个退出的事情吗?
Were you really cool with this whole sign-out thing?

1098
01:05:15,874 --> 01:05:20,337
严重吗?我已经罚了我的铺位，还让他们把所有的道具都退了。
Seriously? I already punished my bunk and made them return all the props.

1099
01:05:20,420 --> 01:05:21,504
但是你怎么了?
But what's up with you?

1100
01:05:21,588 --> 01:05:24,382
当我第一次听说你今年夏天要来的时候
You know, when I first heard you were coming this summer,

1101
01:05:24,466 --> 01:05:26,176
见到你我很兴奋。
I was excited to see you.

1102
01:05:26,259 --> 01:05:28,511
我以为我们之间的争执已经过去了
I thought we'd be past whatever beef we had

1103
01:05:28,595 --> 01:05:32,223
我们可以…朋友了。
and we could just be... friends again.

1104
01:05:32,307 --> 01:05:35,226
你说得倒容易。
That is so easy for you to say.

1105
01:05:35,310 --> 01:05:38,813
当你抛弃我时，我一无所有，而你拥有一切。
I got nothing and you got everything when you dropped me.

1106
01:05:38,897 --> 01:05:39,939
我放弃了你?
I dropped you?

1107
01:05:40,023 --> 01:05:42,817
-你背叛了我-我从没背叛过你。
- You cheated on me. - I never cheated on you.

1108
01:05:42,901 --> 01:05:44,444
你欺骗了我们。
You cheated on our act.

1109
01:05:45,153 --> 01:05:49,949
”凯。好吧，我承认。我背着你参加了那个电视会议。
'Kay. Yes, fine, I'll admit it. I took that TV meeting behind your back.

1110
01:05:50,033 --> 01:05:52,744
你总是叫我你的门徒。
You were always calling me your protégée.

1111
01:05:52,827 --> 01:05:54,621
我想看看我自己能不能做到。
I wanted to see if I could do it on my own.

1112
01:05:54,704 --> 01:05:57,540
你的背叛终于被揭露了。
Your treachery is finally revealed.

1113
01:05:57,624 --> 01:06:01,169
是的。他们认为我在电视上独自表演会更好。
Yes. They thought I would be a better solo act on TV.

1114
01:06:01,252 --> 01:06:03,296
他们讨厌Abraca-Duo这个名字。
And they hated the name Abraca-Duo.

1115
01:06:03,380 --> 01:06:04,547
当时它很吸引人!
It was catchy at the time!

1116
01:06:04,631 --> 01:06:06,341
-但我拒绝了——到底!
- But I told them no. - Exactly!

1117
01:06:06,424 --> 01:06:07,842
什么?
What?

1118
01:06:08,426 --> 01:06:10,970
我告诉他们我不是一个独角戏演员。
I told them I wasn't a solo act.

1119
01:06:11,054 --> 01:06:13,431
我想为我们俩谈点条件
I was trying to negotiate a deal for the both of us,

1120
01:06:13,515 --> 01:06:15,767
但我还没来得及解释你就辞职了。
but you quit before I could explain.

1121
01:06:18,186 --> 01:06:20,814
——为什么……你为什么不阻止我?-因为你发疯了。
- Why... Why didn't you stop me? - 'Cause you were flipping out.

1122
01:06:20,897 --> 01:06:23,066
你不回我的电话和短信。
You wouldn't return any of my phone calls or texts.

